[
  {
    "startTime": 0.266,
    "endTime": 1.568,
    "text": "Now I thought I'd share some of my favorite --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1.568,
    "endTime": 4.27,
    "text": "\"My Weird Superstition\" stories from you guys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.27,
    "endTime": 8.7,
    "text": "Here we go. This first one's from @JesseBetts11."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.7,
    "endTime": 10.75,
    "text": "He says, \"Whenever I'm home alone,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.76,
    "endTime": 10.877,
    "text": "I always say, 'I see you'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.877,
    "endTime": 14.18,
    "text": "before falling asleep just to see if anyone responds.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.18,
    "endTime": 16.816,
    "text": "[ Laughter and applause ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.816,
    "endTime": 18.284,
    "text": "\"Okay, okay. Then I'll leave then."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.284,
    "endTime": 20.82,
    "text": "You can see me? I thought I was hiding but --\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.82,
    "endTime": 23.69,
    "text": "-Yeah. -\"All right.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.69,
    "endTime": 27.93,
    "text": "This one's from @hasasimo."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.93,
    "endTime": 29.496,
    "text": "He says, \"My brother-in-law doesn't allow his mother"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.496,
    "endTime": 31.464,
    "text": "into the room if the Dallas Cowboys are winning."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.464,
    "endTime": 34.234,
    "text": "If she's already in the room, he doesn't let her leave."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.234,
    "endTime": 36.690000000000005,
    "text": "He's done this for over 20 years."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.69,
    "endTime": 39.739,
    "text": "The cowboys haven't been to a Super Bowl in over 20 years.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.739,
    "endTime": 42.739999999999995,
    "text": "[ Laughter and applause ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.75,
    "endTime": 45.211,
    "text": "Hey, leave your mom alone!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.211,
    "endTime": 47.58,
    "text": "-It's his fault. -Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.58,
    "endTime": 50.85,
    "text": "This one's from @NicolaFry1980."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.85,
    "endTime": 52.685,
    "text": "She says, \"When I take painkillers,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.685,
    "endTime": 54.521,
    "text": "I have to whisper what's wrong with me first"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.521,
    "endTime": 56.189,
    "text": "like 'headache' or 'sore shoulder,'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.189,
    "endTime": 58.458,
    "text": "or else the medicine won't know where to go.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.458,
    "endTime": 60.86,
    "text": "[ Laughter and applause ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.86,
    "endTime": 62.695,
    "text": "\"Sore shoulder.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.695,
    "endTime": 66.599,
    "text": "-Mnh. -I like that one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.599,
    "endTime": 69.936,
    "text": "This one's from @RunningUnicorns."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.936,
    "endTime": 71.638,
    "text": "Ohh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.638,
    "endTime": 72.305,
    "text": "How quaint."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.305,
    "endTime": 74.908,
    "text": "She says, \"I never eat the first Pringle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.908,
    "endTime": 77.21000000000001,
    "text": "in a can, that' s the barrier Pringle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.21,
    "endTime": 79.312,
    "text": "I throw it away every time.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.312,
    "endTime": 81.214,
    "text": "[ Laughter and applause ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.214,
    "endTime": 83.283,
    "text": "-What? Oh, yeah. -Yeah, no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.283,
    "endTime": 85.752,
    "text": "\"No, no, no, that's the barrier Pringle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.752,
    "endTime": 86.786,
    "text": "Unh-unh. Nice try!\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.786,
    "endTime": 88.455,
    "text": "-That's got factory germs on it. -\"Nice try."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.455,
    "endTime": 90.89,
    "text": "I don't want anything to do with that one.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.89,
    "endTime": 92.292,
    "text": "[ Laughter ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.292,
    "endTime": 94.961,
    "text": "This one's from @timeofbacon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.961,
    "endTime": 95.695,
    "text": "[ Laughter ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.695,
    "endTime": 96.595,
    "text": "-Time of bacon. -Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.596,
    "endTime": 101.101,
    "text": "He says, \"Any time someone on TV winks, I have to wink back.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.101,
    "endTime": 103.703,
    "text": "[ Laughter and applause ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.703,
    "endTime": 106.10600000000001,
    "text": "[ Audience cheering ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.106,
    "endTime": 107.94,
    "text": "\"I see you!\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.941,
    "endTime": 112.512,
    "text": "\"Who?!\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.512,
    "endTime": 115.181,
    "text": "This one's from @motownphyllie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.181,
    "endTime": 116.916,
    "text": "She says -- This is great. -What'd she say?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.916,
    "endTime": 118.985,
    "text": "\"When I was little, my mom told me that every grain"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.985,
    "endTime": 120.787,
    "text": "of rice I didn't finish in my dinner bowl"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.787,
    "endTime": 123.49000000000001,
    "text": "would be a zit on my future husband's face.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.49,
    "endTime": 126.24,
    "text": "[ Audience \"ohhs\", laughter ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.25,
    "endTime": 127.794,
    "text": "[ Laughter and applause ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.794,
    "endTime": 130.964,
    "text": "What?! Oh, my goodness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.964,
    "endTime": 133.133,
    "text": "-Wow. -Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.133,
    "endTime": 137.3,
    "text": "This one's from @DarolineCavrnas."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.3,
    "endTime": 138.537,
    "text": "She says, \"I had a bad case of the hiccups,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.538,
    "endTime": 141.741,
    "text": "and they finally went away when I talked about Sandra Bullock."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.741,
    "endTime": 144.21,
    "text": "Now my brother and I will discuss Sandra Bullock"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.21,
    "endTime": 147.31300000000002,
    "text": "when one of us have hiccups and they always go away.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.313,
    "endTime": 148.515,
    "text": "[ Laughter and applause ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.515,
    "endTime": 151.184,
    "text": "Really? That's the secret?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.184,
    "endTime": 154.353,
    "text": "Stare at a spoon and just think of Sandra Bullock."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.354,
    "endTime": 156.656,
    "text": "Yeah, Bandra Sullock."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.656,
    "endTime": 158.324,
    "text": "[ Laughter ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.324,
    "endTime": 160.26000000000002,
    "text": "[ Hiccups ] You just gave me hiccups."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.26,
    "endTime": 161.361,
    "text": "Yeah, I gave you the hiccups."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.361,
    "endTime": 161.89399999999998,
    "text": "[ Laughter ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.895,
    "endTime": 164.964,
    "text": "This last one's from @rtran1251."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.964,
    "endTime": 166.533,
    "text": "You think that's a robot?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.533,
    "endTime": 167.6,
    "text": "I hope so."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.6,
    "endTime": 170.103,
    "text": "She says, \"I halfway believe in aliens,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.103,
    "endTime": 172.10500000000002,
    "text": "but I try my hardest not to think about them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.105,
    "endTime": 174.641,
    "text": "because if they're real, they for sure read minds"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.641,
    "endTime": 177.60899999999998,
    "text": "and then they'd know that I know that they know.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.61,
    "endTime": 178.44000000000003,
    "text": "Oh. Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.44,
    "endTime": 178.878,
    "text": "[ Laughter and applause ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.878,
    "endTime": 181.47,
    "text": "There you have it, those are \"Tonight Show Hashtags.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.47,
    "endTime": 182.582,
    "text": "To check out more of our favorites,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.582,
    "endTime": 186.92,
    "text": "Go to tonightshow.com/hashtags."
  }
]